803
00:53:56,399 --> 00:53:57,525
Kapan kau bebaskan aku?

804
00:53:58,109 --> 00:53:59,110
Disembunyikan di mana?

805
00:54:00,195 --> 00:54:01,404
Itu rahasia.

806
00:54:02,322 --> 00:54:03,782
Kapan aku bisa ke dunia sana?

